Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel{TYPESET}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise{TYPESET}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've ever worn something this light and cool! {i'm pretty sure this is a line from an old episode. check around episode 15 when they go to buy that dress. i'm too tired to look through old eps right now}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes all of Claudia McCunnen's conspiracies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She trapped me in order to take away my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she used Zwei, who eventually became Phantom, as a toy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and eliminated Wisemel's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her modus operandi is something to be praised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We received a call from Lizzie Garland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia McCunnen has gone into hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like she doesn't plan to give us excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it is unbelievable, Scythe Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can think of it as a corroboration for your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to your suggestion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we must retain the cooperative route with the Godoh Group, which sided with Claudia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year's cocaine robbery was surely a painful memory for Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The profit from the Far Eastern market which the Godoh Group makes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is infinitely higher than the sustained losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, if you apply the "emotional theory,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you will be much more considerate when it comes to Mr. Shiga's decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to purge Godoh Daisuke as soon as the truth was revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is certainly a logical suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the profit that the Godoh Group demands this time will be reduced as a penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:04:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for agitating your men, I assure a most cruel end to Claudia McCunnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. McGuire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are investigating Claudia's whereabouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Phantom is the real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what he'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, Mr. McGuire,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may I send out Ein to track him down?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A duel between the old and the new Phantom, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to work under the Bloodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isaac was the one who killed Romero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new, strong organization is backing the Bloodies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, Inferno's time will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to climb up the ranks that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even by working under your little brother's murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reach where Romero couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that's the best way to pay my respects to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, I don't want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Lizzie Garland.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I am part of the Mafia,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of becoming a human slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a righteousness which is above simple loss and profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you promise not to violate this, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, Clau.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To go on ahead like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a complete imbecile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! Nothing is coming out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Ms. Lizzie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:05:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her car key.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I look at it, the more awesome it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to ride the car owner as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you at least have a gist of what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I simply did what I had to do\Nin order to survive in the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been deceiving you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't plan on giving up just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to escape from L.A. and join the East Coast Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in order to protect myself from Inferno's agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for you at the 39th Drive Inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll put my life in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scars like that can be removed at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I intentionally did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that scar symbolize?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insult and downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, you were my best achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were soiled by that man twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your current self is far from perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am right beside garbage like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is because I believe that the time for renewal will come someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleanse your disgrace with your own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reclaim yourself and recover that light that was within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall remove that scar from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall love you as my creation once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Ein win against Azuma Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the worst-case scenario,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll sacrifice herself in order to kill Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrificing her own life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to use her and then throw her away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to an excellent creation known as Ein,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my art is about to reach a new level.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she is the first full creation that is worth celebrating,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't put that much worth into souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must have been a better method.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, actors overact in plays\Nand the brush moves to an unexpected location.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Muse's prank which surprises both the artist and the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the final stage be a tragedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will it be a happy ending?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To leave the finale's joy to fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that something to be thrilled about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would her disposal be too much for you to handle, Lizzie Garland?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Claudia are old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to your feelings, you might have difficulties pulling the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the fuck up, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:11:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who has no sense of time will become hated, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where it all began.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not Zwei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I doing until now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to race just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Driving at an uncatchable speed, leaving everything behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might end up flying to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you planning to go with all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just go wherever I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, you'll just get tired and stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that point, what will you do when you don't have your legs on the ground anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are stones which can't be left unturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some scenes can only be seen when you race at this speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to chase that to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Till the very end...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die like this? Without doing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're my opponent, then I'm like a rat in a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to win in a proper fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the best shall survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prove worthy of being a true Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, then I'll play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you are given reasons to fight this badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by that Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to win either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To kill you, and run away from this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would change?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get deceived, played with,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and never be able to protect the one that you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this endless loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, finish me off this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing could have been done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can't endure this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you are still alive and can fight your way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now... for that Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:16:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I live is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore to fight for my own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the scar that you made that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I admired you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was just a short moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your strength that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the proof of your oath that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lives on in this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I couldn't throw my life away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are another form of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:18:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fought through the path that I gave up myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You struggled and fought through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I lived dreaming about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,believing that another me is living on freely somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scar has always reminded me of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can no longer endure this pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one can blame you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you are going to break that day's oath...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...kill me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And end everything once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Master's failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a doll that's waiting to be disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this world wasn't a complete hell for for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's because you were alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to live in a world without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, I couldn't keep any promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I still have a promise I must keep, I'd like to keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely my last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you away from Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the ending wasn't so pleasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be too quick to judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps this was really just one act of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treasure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treasure it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I can't go to where you are for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have an unfinished job that I must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that we wouldn't get separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that we would be together...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
